            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        Massachusetts Has a Huge Waitlist for State-Funded Housing. So Why Are 2,300 Units Vacant?
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        Families are stuck in shelters or sleeping in their cars while a flawed state selection process and meager funding for renovations leave apartments empty for years.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--center     " data-pp-location="article meta">

