    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/russian-politician-who-reportedly-sent-millions-to-nra-has-long-history-in-spain">
                                    Russian Politician Who Reportedly Sent Millions to NRA Has Long History in Spain
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Spanish authorities were poised to arrest Alexander Torshin in a money-laundering case in 2013 when he mysteriously canceled his trip to Spain.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sebastian-rotella">Sebastian Rotella</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2018-01-19EST17:01">Jan. 19, 2018, 5:01 p.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                            </div>
            </ol> <!-- end .most-read-group -->

</div> <!-- end .most-read -->



    
